data.description:
PRICE REDUCTION.... Seller is motivated to sell and is offering $5,000 towards Buyer closing cost, bring us your offer!  This delightful earth contact home located just minutes from Warrensburg, a prime location. Only a short drive to outdoor recreational opportunities, shopping/dining options, and UCM College, the home also offers a short commute to Whiteman Airforce Base. As if that's not enough, you'll also enjoy privacy of the 6 acres of woodlands, the swimming pool, outdoor living space.
This country neighborhood with low-traffic roads that are framed by greenery and trees.
The large yard is attractively landscaped. A classic duo of exterior amenities, the clear blue above ground pool and the solid floor patio go together to create the most inviting summer day. Also in the yard there is a private patio off master suite.
Tray ceilings top the room with sense of luxury. Stylish fixtures contribute to the elegant atmosphere. The open floor plan is great for elbow room, and never goes out of style. You will enjoy the picturesque warmth in the glow of the Stone fireplaces in the living room. The Kitchen is Spacious and newly updated, this kitchen is an efficient galley layout with lots of beautiful wood cabinet for plenty of storage and counter space.
The ensuite primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor. This bedroom has double closets and electric fireplace and double doors that lead to a private patio. The private bathroom includes a large walk-in shower.  There is another bedroom and a non-conforming bedroom/office and guest bathroom on the main level, all unique and rich with closet space. Your laundry room and a half bath are conveniently located off the kitchen.  2 bedrooms, a kitchenet and family room are located on the upper level of the the home above the garage. 
An attached 2 car garage with workshop area is especially convenient in bad weather. There are so many great amenities to love about this home.
